      <article role="article" about="/contact/careers" typeof="schema:WebPage" class="page full clearfix">

  
      <span property="schema:name" content="Careers" class="hidden"></span>


  
  <div class="content">
    
            <div property="schema:text" class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden field--item"><h2><strong>Rockstars</strong> wanted!</h2>

<p>Make your mark in the exciting world of open source innovation with Valuebound, leaders in Drupal CMS services par excellence. To join the prestigious international Drupal community through a promising career offering stimulating learning and exciting growth opportunities, join us now!</p>

<h2>Sales &amp; Marketing Associate (Mid Level)</h2>

<p><strong>Location:</strong> Bangalore - <strong>Department:</strong> Marketing</p>

<p>Are you the looking for long-term sales and marketing career and not just job? Are you looking for turning your personal skill into your competitive advantage? Valuebound has been recognized as top Drupal service provider in world, serving both FORTUNE 500® and emerging companies throughout the United States and India from our team of experience and community recognised developers.</p>

<p>We are looking for entrepreneurial individuals just like you to serve as Sales and Marketing Associates and be part of our next growth story. In this mid level position, you will learn and take the lead role in acquiring new clients and taking ownership to expand into new markets. This will require meeting face-to-face as well as virtual with both existing and new potential business customers.</p>

<p>You will receive comprehensive on the job training to hone your skills and ensure your success with us.</p>

<p>Here is just some of what we have to offer:</p>

<ul><li>A fast-paced, fun work environment where we respect each other</li>
	<li>Performance-based career growth opportunities and we are serious about this.</li>
	<li>Personal and professional growth. We beDelivery coordination, UAT coordination</li>
</ul><p>If you have the urge and personality of persistence which is quality of top Sales and Marketing Associate, we have a rewarding career opportunity to take advantage of your skill sets. Successful candidate for this position can be from a variety of different background, education and experiences.</p>

<p>Here is what we’re looking for in a top candidate:</p>

<ul><li>Strong verbal and written communication skills</li>
	<li>A desire to grow both professionally and personally.</li>
	<li>Constant learner's mentality</li>
	<li>Upbeat and optimistic attitude</li>
	<li>Demonstrable competitive nature</li>
	<li>Demonstrable leadership capabilities</li>
	<li>MBA degree preferred, but not required</li>
</ul><p>If this sounds interesting and you have waiting for a career move, and if you meet our qualification, we want to hear from you. You can email us today at <a href="mailto:elora.dash@valuehrservices.com">elora.dash@valuehrservices.com</a></p>

<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="mailto:careers@valuebound.com">Apply Now</a></p>

<h2><br />
PHP / Drupal Developer (Experience: 1-4 Years)</h2>

<p><strong>Location:</strong> Bangalore - <strong>Department:</strong> Engineering</p>

<p>We are looking for candidates having exposure and experience in the following skill sets:</p>

<ul><li>Good experience in PHP programming, Javascript, Ajax, html &amp; CSS.</li>
	<li>Good knowledge of Drupal 6.x / 7.x</li>
	<li>Must be able to develop prototypes in Drupal for desired functions</li>
	<li>Delivery coordination, UAT coordination</li>
</ul><p><strong>Main Job Tasks and Responsibilities </strong></p>

<ul><li>Build web sites, pages, themes, page elements, landing pages, XML documents, and other types of content as needed.</li>
	<li>Develop custom theme work with Drupal, Drupal Drupal !</li>
	<li>Develop custom modules that integrate with existing modules</li>
	<li>Support, maintain, and existing client sites</li>
	<li>Mad Skills with CSS, HTML, PHP, MYSQL, JavaScript, and other web programming language as needed. More are always welcome</li>
	<li>Potentially meet with client to explain and provide key information on projects and process</li>
</ul><p> </p>

<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="mailto:careers@valuebound.com">Apply Now</a></p>

<h2><strong>Community Relationship Manager</strong></h2>

<p><strong>Location:</strong> Bangalore</p>

<p><span><strong>Employment type</strong>:<span> </span></span><span>Full time</span><br /><br />
We are looking for candidates having exposure and experience in the following skill sets:</p>

<ul><li>Extrovert, Excellent Written &amp; Verbal Communication skill, Pleasant Personality</li>
	<li>You should know how to strike conversation with people.</li>
	<li>Will be of added advantage if you can write blog promoting these events</li>
</ul><p><strong>Main Job Tasks and Responsibilities </strong></p>

<ul><li>Planning, developing and implementing strategies for growing Drupal developer community in Bangalore</li>
	<li>Raise awareness in the student community about Drupal as preferred career choice</li>
	<li>Help community to plan and schedule Free Drupal training events in top engineering colleges in Bangalore</li>
	<li>Managing incoming inquiries from students as well as other developers</li>
	<li>Liaison with Drupal team from other companies to encourage their participation in community activities</li>
</ul><p><strong>Education: </strong>No limitation.</p>

<p><a class="btn btn-default" href="mailto:elora.dash@valuehrservices.com">Apply Now</a></p>
</div>
      
